Package model

Class Commander

java.lang.Object
model.Commander
public class Commander extends Object
This class is used to instantiate a Commander, which is used as a basic user model.

  • Constructor Details

    • Commander

      public Commander​(String login, String commanderName, String realName, SortedMap<Attribute,​Integer> attributes, int points, boolean isAdmin)
      Primary constructor for Commander class.
      Parameters:
      login - Login ID used for logging and referring to the commander.
      commanderName - Commander name as used in game.
      realName - "Real" GDR name, used for roleplay purposes.
      attributes - SortedMap of Attribute, which stores the attributes of the commander.
      points - Points the Commander has.
      isAdmin - Whether this Commander has admin privileges or not.

      public int getPoints()

    • setPoints

      public void setPoints​(int points)
      Setter method for the points.
      Parameters:
      points - The points of the Commander, given as int. If negative, the points are set to 0.

    • addPoints

      public void addPoints​(int points)
      Utility method for adjusting the points of the Commander.
      Parameters:
      points - Points to be added or subtracted. If the Commander would have a negative amount of points, they become 0.

    • isAdmin
